{310}{}{那么，我在和谁说话？ -- So, who am I talking to?}
#{311}{}{To me, obviously. I think I'd rather hear *your* name first.}
{311}{}{对我来说，很明显。我想我还是先听听你的名字吧。 -- To me, obviously. I think I'd rather hear *your* name first.}
#{312}{}{My name is }
{312}{}{我的名字是 -- My name is }
#{313}{}{. And you are...}
{313}{}{. 你是。。。 -- . And you are...}
