#{450}{}{Why does Hal Wallace hate you?}
{450}{}{哈尔・华莱士为什么恨你？ -- Why does Hal Wallace hate you?}
#{451}{}{What? What are you talking about?}
{451}{}{什么？你在说什么？ -- What? What are you talking about?}
